history.content:
Hello all,
HackDavis 2019 is a 24-hour long coding event, happening on February 9th - 10th, 2019, that helps address some of the most pressing issues related to the Environment, Health, and Education.
They have extended their application deadline to THIS FRIDAY January 11 @ 11:59pm. Apply at https://hackdavis.io. 
This event is free for all admitted participants and people of all programming levels and all majors are welcome. There will be free food and swag, and you will also have access to mentors from many different companies who will host workshops and help guide you. A hackathon is an amazing opportunity to challenge yourself to learn something completely new, such as making a web server, controlling a drone, or even reading brain waves! 
Feel free to contact HackDavis at team@hackdavis.io if you have any questions.
If you haven't already, check us out on social media: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HackDavis/?ref=bookmarks
Event Page: https://www.facebook.com/events/2208194569464086/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hackdavis/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/hack_davis
Medium: https://medium.com/@HackDavis
